How Music Affects Our Productivity

When do people listen to music?

Listening occurs throughout the day, but it seems like people most often listen to music around 15:00 and 17:00.

Do people use different genres for different tasks?

11 participants said Yes, and 2 said No to listening to different genres for different activities.

Productivity by activity

The average productivity across all activities was 8.1.

The most productive activity was Doing chores with an average score of 10, and the least productive activity was Shower with an average score of 7.

What genres are popular for different activities?

The top 3 most frequent genres and their associated top activities are:

  • Instrumental : Studying/Working

  • Pop : Commuting

  • R&B : Commuting

Productivity by genre

It seemed like genres like Rock had the highest average productivity scores.
